TitMainTitle: Group portrait of wedding party with two flower girls, one ring bearer, four men, and five women standing, including groom, wearing light colored bow tie and light colored carnation on left lapel, and bride, wearing headpiece with mid length veil, earrings, long sleeved satin wedding dress with floral lace overlay around collar and long train, holding bouquet of roses, posed in front of plants in interior with portraits of men on walls and geometrically patterned rug, possibly for wedding on Wheeler Street in McKees Rocks
